al/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yJjazvJiGwM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyJjazvJiGwM&d=Uv6DBE72f%2B4kC1FBSpfbt%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3b46da0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yJjazvJiGwM</a>"},{"pid":"c22d8069949147a4289f2e34d9b8524f07a41132","tid":294641,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請出招</blockquote><br />\n入門<br />\n<br />\n音源：Creepy Nuts - 合法的トビ方ノススメ<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UVaZf3GliDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUVaZf3GliDs&d=Uv6DBE72f%2B4kC1FBSpfbt%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d063a5d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UVaZf3GliDs</a><br />\n<br />\nBattle：ADERNALINE 2014 R-指定vsGOLBY<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xvhB_qUlfJ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxvhB_qUlfJ4&d=Uv6DBE72f%2B4kC1FBSpfbt%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=371266c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xvhB_qUlfJ4</a><br />\n<br />\nR-指定係日本最大既MC Battle大會 UMB既皇者<br />\n曾經達成 地方預選(大阪)5連霸(2010-2014) 本選3連霸(2012-2014) <br />\n係一個全能型既Rapper<br />\n<br />\n比賽上，無論係Rhyme, Flow, Beat Approach, 同埋即興Answer既質素都係非常高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n音樂上，佢同全國DJ大賽第2名既DJ松永組左個叫Creepy Nuts既組合<br />\n佢地既歌唔拘泥於Hard Core既hip hop<br />\n例如上面果首就係講就算唔靠大麻，靠聽佢地既hip hop都一樣high得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而上面既比賽片段就睇得出<br />\n全盛期既R-指定既即興押韻有幾癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHard Core少少<br />\n<br />\n音源：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/onTKv0A44PA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FonTKv0A44PA&d=Uv6DBE72f%2B4kC1FBSpfbt%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=51dca7cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/onTKv0A44PA</a><br />\n<br />\n呂布カルマ係一個特別既MC<br />\n歌既特色係好似詩一樣既用字<br />\n比賽上唔拘泥於押韻，但其實好多時都有押唔易察覺既韻，UMB2016亞軍<br />\n上面係講述呂布カルマ自己既一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBattle：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u-9BpRqZQS0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu-9BpRqZQS0&d=Uv6DBE72f%2B4kC1FBSpfbt%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1bc6a79c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/u-9BpRqZQS0</a><br />\n<br />\nMOL53係現今MC battle入面比較體現到&ldquo;Hip Hop&rdquo;既一個MC<br />\nBeat Approach做得非常好<br />\n亦都成日強調自己係一個貨真價實，屬於Underground既Rapper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}